From: Peter Jung <admin@ptr1337.dev>
Date: Tue, 3 Feb 2026 20:42:49 +0100
Subject: [PATCH 22/22] usb: core: add USB_QUIRK_NO_BOS for additional capture
 devices

Add the USB_QUIRK_NO_BOS quirk for several USB capture cards that hang
when attempting to fetch the BOS descriptor at SuperSpeed Plus:

  - ASUS TUF 4K PRO (0b05:1ab9)
  - Avermedia Live Gamer Ultra 2.1 GC553G2 (07ca:2553)
  - UGREEN 35871 (2b89:5871)

 These devices exhibit the same behavior as the Elgato 4K X, where the
 BOS descriptor request causes the device to become unresponsive.

Signed-off-by: Peter Jung <admin@ptr1337.dev>
---
 drivers/usb/core/quirks.c | 9 +++++++++
 1 file changed, 9 insertions(+)

diff --git a/drivers/usb/core/quirks.c b/drivers/usb/core/quirks.c
index c4d85089d..ddce45ce9 100644
--- a/drivers/usb/core/quirks.c
+++ b/drivers/usb/core/quirks.c
@@ -453,6 +453,15 @@ static const struct usb_device_id usb_quirk_list[] = {
 	/* Elgato 4K X - BOS descriptor fetch hangs at SuperSpeed Plus */
 	{ USB_DEVICE(0x0fd9, 0x009b), .driver_info = USB_QUIRK_NO_BOS },
 
+	/* ASUS TUF 4K PRO - BOS descriptor fetch hangs at SuperSpeed Plus */
+	{ USB_DEVICE(0x0b05, 0x1ab9), .driver_info = USB_QUIRK_NO_BOS },
+
+	/* Avermedia Live Gamer Ultra 2.1 (GC553G2) - BOS descriptor fetch hangs at SuperSpeed Plus */
+	{ USB_DEVICE(0x07ca, 0x2553), .driver_info = USB_QUIRK_NO_BOS },
+
+	/* UGREEN 35871 - BOS descriptor fetch hangs at SuperSpeed Plus */
+	{ USB_DEVICE(0x2b89, 0x5871), .driver_info = USB_QUIRK_NO_BOS },
+
 	/* Sony Xperia XZ1 Compact (lilac) smartphone in fastboot mode */
 	{ USB_DEVICE(0x0fce, 0x0dde), .driver_info = USB_QUIRK_NO_LPM },
 
